  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_459996243" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/459996243" />
    <a title="Paul" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/750164-paul"><img alt="Paul" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1218596224p2/750164.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/459996243?book_show_action=true">Nov 20, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Paul" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Paul" href="/user/show/750164-paul">Paul</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer459996243" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4287071202968296427">This was a well-researched, thorough history of the late 1920s and 1930s, but it was book that didn&apos;t explain a lot of cause-and-effect of the policies of the Roosevelt administration and why it pertains to today&apos;s politics. She presented the facts but didn&apos;t seem to connect the dots, in other words.</span>
  <span id="freeText4287071202968296427" style="display:none">This was a well-researched, thorough history of the late 1920s and 1930s, but it was book that didn't explain a lot of cause-and-effect of the policies of the Roosevelt administration and why it pertains to today's politics. She presented the facts but didn't seem to connect the dots, in other words.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4287071202968296427" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
