<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5249492-new-deal-or-raw-deal"><img alt="New Deal or Raw Deal?: How FDR&#39;s Economic Legacy Has Damaged America" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1347694389l/5249492._SX98_.jpg" />
